==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: To be one basket (of dirt) short of success (in one's attempt to build a nine [[仞|ren]] high mound).

From the longer phrase (first part is usually omitted):

[[为]][[山]][[九]][[仞]]，[[功]][[亏]][[一]][[篑]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: gōng kuī yī kuì

===Idiom===
'''[[功]][[亏]][[一]][[篑]]'''

# [[close but no cigar]]; [[close, but no cigar]].

===Alternate forms===
[[功虧一簣]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

===Related terms===
*[[功败垂成]]
*[[半途而废]]
*[[前功尽弃]]

